{"tha-ap380:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap380:0.2":"Bodhivandanavagga ","tha-ap380:0.3":"Sumanatalavantiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap380:1.1":"“Siddhatthassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap380:1.2":"talavantamadasaham; ","tha-ap380:1.3":"Sumanehi paticchannam, ","tha-ap380:1.4":"dharayami maharaham. ","tha-ap380:2.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap380:2.2":"talavantamadasaham; ","tha-ap380:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap380:2.4":"talavantassidam phalam. ","tha-ap380:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap380:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap380:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap380:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap380:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap380:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap380:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap380:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap380:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap380:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sumanatalavantiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap380:7.1":"Sumanatalavantiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}